<placeName cert="high">Oxyrhynchus</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/><del rend="erasure"><expan><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">λ</unclear>όγ<ex cert="high">ος</ex></expan> Μαξίμου</del> 

    <lb n="2"/>κυρίῳ <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">μου ἀδ</supplied>ελφῷ Ἀ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">μμ</unclear>ωνί<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ῳ</unclear> 

    <lb n="3"/>Σαρ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear>πάμμων χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="4"/>ἀπήντησεν πρὸς σὲ ὁ ἀδελφὸς 

    <lb n="5"/>ἡμῶν Δωρόθεος ἀ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ξ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ι</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ω</unclear>θεὶς <hi rend="diaeresis">ὑ</hi>π᾽ ἐ-

    <lb n="6"/>μοῦ ὥστε αὐτὸν <choice><corr>ἀπαιτῆσαι</corr><sic><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">απ</unclear>ετησαι</sic></choice> τὰς <choice><corr>ἐχθέσεις</corr><sic>εχθεσις</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="7"/>τὰς λοιπαζομένας τῆς <choice><corr>τετάρ<supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">της</supplied></corr><sic>τεταρ</sic></choice> ἰνδικτίωνος. 

    <lb n="8"/>οἶδας <choice><corr>ὅτι</corr><sic>οθι</sic></choice> καὶ τὰ ἐνέχυρα <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἡ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">μ</supplied>ῶν ἔ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ξ</unclear>ω εἰσὶν 

    <lb n="9"/>καὶ ὁ πατὴρ ἡμῶν Διόσκορος ἔχρησεν ἡμῖν 

    <lb n="10"/>κα<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὶ</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear>ὐ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τὸν</unclear> θέλομεν πληρῶσαι· διὸ σπουδή σοι 

    <lb n="11"/>γε<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear>έσθω συ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">νβαλ</unclear>έσθαι αὐτῷ μετὰ καὶ τῶν 

    <lb n="12"/>συμμάχων ἄχ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ρ</supplied>ις οὗ ἂν τὴν <choice><corr>ἀπαίτησιν</corr><sic>α<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">π</supplied>ετησιν</sic></choice> ποιή-

    <lb n="13"/>σῃ τῆς τετάρ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">η</supplied>ς <hi rend="diaeresis">ἰ</hi>νδικτίωνος· αὐτὸς γὰρ 

    <lb n="14"/>καὶ τὸν λόγον <subst><add place="inline">αὐτῶν</add><del rend="corrected">αυτος</del></subst> δ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ύ</unclear>ναται εἰδέναι 

    <lb n="15"/>καὶ διὰ τοῦτο ἠξίωσα αὐτὸν ἀπαντῆσαι 

    <lb n="16"/>καὶ τὴν <choice><corr>ἀπαίτησιν</corr><sic>απετησιν</sic></choice> <choice><corr>ποιῆσαι</corr><sic>ποιηση</sic></choice> <hi rend="diaeresis">ἵ</hi>να δυνηθῶ-

    <lb n="17"/>μεν καὶ Διόσκορον πληρῶ-

    <lb n="18"/>σαι καὶ τὰ ἐνέχυρα ἡμῶν ἀνα-

    <lb n="19"/>κομισώμεθα. μὴ οὖν ὀκνήσῃς συνβαλέ-

    <lb n="20"/>σθαι αὐτῷ μετὰ καὶ τῶν συμμάχων ἄχρις 

    <lb n="21"/>οὗ <subst><add place="inline">ἂν</add><del rend="corrected">τν</del></subst> τὴν <choice><corr>ἀπαίτησιν</corr><sic>απετησιν</sic></choice> ποιήσῃ. ἐρρῶ-

    <lb n="22"/>σθαί σε εὔχομαι πολλοῖς 

    <lb n="23"/>χρόνοις, <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἄδελ</unclear>φε. </ab></div><div n="meta.33725" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.33725" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="400" notBefore="301" type="textDate">IV</date></p></div><div n="meta.33725" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Gehört zum Archiv der Brüder Papnuthis und Dorotheos.</p></div><div n="meta.33725" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">48</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">3419</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">33725</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">48</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">3419</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0181;48;3419" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.33725" part="N" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">270</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">IX</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">202</biblScope></bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.33725" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.33725" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="high" type="ancientFindspot">Oxyrhynchos</placeName></p></div><div n="meta.33725" part="N" type="figure"><p><figure href="http://163.1.169.40/cgi-bin/library?e=d-000-00---0POxy--00-0-0-0prompt-10---4---Document---0-1l--1-en-50---20-about---001-001-1-0utfZz-8-00031-001-1-0utfZz-8-00&amp;a=d&amp;c=POxy&amp;cl=CL5.1.14&amp;d=HASH01f92445de7b96527d6a1cc3"><figDesc>Abbil